OL,10,     Gself-portraiture together.
OL,11,G0530FAuction: Shakespeare Special
OL,12,     GMore than 400 years after his
OL,13,     Gdeath, an example of the
OL,14,     Gcelebrated playwright's completed
OL,15,     Gwork - The First Folio - is up
OL,16,     Gfor auction at Christie's in New
OL,17,     GYork and could fetch millions.
